ygData.subject: Re: [eqbards] Kunark Songs
ygData.msgSnippet: I ve been using the chant series like CRAZY in Kunark with almost 0 resists.  On the other hand, the few times I ve whipped out my Kisch, I think I ve had 100%
ygData.messageBody:
I've been using the chant series like CRAZY in Kunark with almost 0 resists. On the other hand, the few
times I've whipped out my Kisch, I think I've had 100% resists against its poison proc (which is almost
never resisted on Antonica). Perhaps it is the type of the Kunark mob you are fighting? Perhaps too it
is charisma related. Currently I'm up to a whopping 160 unbuffed now.
